                        h1 Apply
                        p.
                            We need a great team to pull off the magic of camp!
                        p.
                            We run day camps 9am-3pm, Monday - Friday, for ages 5-13. Campers are rotated through
                            activities such as crafts, snack, horses and games in groups with a counselor lead.
                            The minimum age for employment is 16 years.
                        p Our positions include:
                        ul
                            li 
                              a(href='campcounselor.html') Camp Counselor
                            li 
