                            li Activity Leader
                        p If you think you'd be a good fit for any of our positions, apply for the 2021 season! The application will be available beginning on March 3, 2021.
                        button(type="button", onclick="window.open('http://www.ultracamp.com/info/sessiondetail.aspx?idCamp=1075&campCode=WWR&idSession=306797', '_blank')") New Staff Application
                        button(type="button", onclick="window.open('http://www.ultracamp.com/info/sessiondetail.aspx?idCamp=1075&campCode=WWR&idSession=308628', '_blank')") Returning Staff Application
                        button(type="button", onclick="window.open('https://www.ultracamp.com/clientlogin.aspx?idCamp=1075&campCode=WWR', '_blank')") Manage Account
                        p Click on the above links to fill out the application that applies to you. This is the same system that we use for camper registration, so there are a few peculiarities you should be aware of. When it is your first time creating an account you will click on New User, then select Individual/Family as your type. Select yourself to register and then confirm your info. Choose "other" as your Role. Fill out all forms in the application. You will then come to the checkout, there is no cost to apply so just continue. You will receive an email confirmation after your application is received. The next step is to schedule an interview, this will appear as a task notification in your account. We are excited to meet you and see if you are a good fit for our team!  
